                <div type="edition" xml:lang="x-oldkhmer-Latn">
<div type="textpart" n="A"><head xml:lang="eng">Face</head>
   <p>
      <lb n="A1"/>. . . . . yajamāna ta vraḥ kaṁmratāṅ· Añ· ta Acas· kñum·
      <lb n="A2"/>. . . . . s· I va dharmma I ku sṅat· I kon· ku ku snehāvali I ku syā-
      <lb n="A3"/>. . . . . joṅ· I kon· ku va khaṇadās· I ku mālavī I tmur· dne[[ṁ]] II
      <lb n="A4"/>. . . (bh)[ai] 80 snā teṁ bhai 100 sru bhai 200 $circleTarget vraḥ kanmi[[ṅ]] kuruṅ· Añ·
   </p>
</div>
<div type="textpart" n="B"><head xml:lang="eng">Face</head>
<p>
<lb n="B1"/>. . . (p)[o]ñ· kloñ· kroṁ ta Ācāryya yajamāna pas· ja[ṁ]nau tam·
   <lb n="B2"/>. . . . t(a) paṁnos· taṅo vraha ta vraḥ kanmiṅ· kñu[[ṁ]] Aṁmraḥ vā kumāradā-
   <lb n="B3"/>[s·?] . . . . . s· I ku pat· pyor· I ku palavī I toṅ· teṁ bhai 40 snā teṁ bhai 80
   <lb n="B4"/>. . . . . lā Ācāryya yajamāna cāturjātakapramāna $circleTarget
</p>
                   </div>
                </div>
                <div type="apparatus">
               <listApp>
